channel.description:
[url]https://skyrim-online.com/[/url]
Not exactly feature filled atm, but since it's first person and based on an actual TES game, I already like it a lot more than ESO.

item.title: Skyrim MP Mod
item.dc:creator: Bloodshot
item.description:
Even at this stage, It’s kind of cool to be able to see people running around. Now you can show off your equipment to your friend in game rather then having to take a screenshot.

Now if they could just get everything else synced.

Honestly, as early as this is it’s exciting they got this far. Every MP mod for a TES game usually gets barely farther then an NPC that jerks around the gameworld, so the only TES game that I’ve been able to play with someone was Battlespire.

I feel like donating
